- Framework: Next.js 14 with App Router
- Database: PostgreSQL via Prisma ORM
- API Layer: /app/api/users/route.ts and /app/api/metrics/route.ts
- State Management: React Query for server state
- Existing pattern: See /app/components/UserCard.tsx for how we structure user data

